; Regression test for issue #1692: Output breaks accounting equation
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1692
;
; Inferred balancing amounts whose magnitude was less than the
; commodity's display precision were compared equal to zero via
; amount_t::is_zero(), even though the value was non-zero at the
; recovered cost precision.  Balance and register output then silently
; omitted the balancing posting, violating double-entry accounting.
;
; Two scenarios trigger this:
;
;   - A new commodity (default display precision 0) participating only
;     as a cost; the inferred balance has fractional digits the
;     commodity has never seen explicitly.  This is the report's
;     original reproducer (`2 X @ 0.2 Y` -> -0.4 Y dropped).
;
;   - An established commodity whose display precision is coarser than
;     the cost's; the inferred balance has digits below the displayed
;     precision (`D 10.00 N` followed by `2 M @ 0.0002 N` -> -0.0004 N
;     dropped at display precision 2).
;
; The fix tags the inferred amount with BIGINT_COST_PREC via
; set_cost_precision() and teaches amount_t::is_zero() and
; amount_t::print() to honour the recovered precision when the
; commodity's display precision would otherwise drop the value to
; zero on the page (or when the commodity has no established
; precision).  The display-time check is what allows the same
; mechanism to handle both scenarios uniformly.  BIGINT_COST_PREC must
; not propagate through addition/subtraction, or running-total
; residuals would inherit it (see issue #717 rounding adjustments).

D 10.00 N

2018-01-01 * Foo
    Assets:A                    2 X @ 0.2 Y
    Assets:B

2018-02-01 * Bar
    Assets:C                    2 M @ 0.0002 N
    Assets:D

test bal
                 2 M
           -0.0004 N
                 2 X
               Y-0.4  Assets
                 2 X    A
               Y-0.4    B
                 2 M    C
           -0.0004 N    D
--------------------
                 2 M
           -0.0004 N
                 2 X
               Y-0.4
end test

test reg
18-Jan-01 Foo                   Assets:A                        2 X          2 X
                                Assets:B                      Y-0.4          2 X
                                                                           Y-0.4
18-Feb-01 Bar                   Assets:C                        2 M          2 M
                                                                             2 X
                                                                           Y-0.4
                                Assets:D                  -0.0004 N          2 M
                                                                       -0.0004 N
                                                                             2 X
                                                                           Y-0.4
end test

test print
2018/01/01 * Foo
    Assets:A                                     2 X @ Y0.2
    Assets:B

2018/02/01 * Bar
    Assets:C                                     2 M @ 0.0002 N
    Assets:D
end test
